Mu matora y’abadepite yo mu 2003 yatorewe kuba umwe mu bagize umutwe w’abadepite ku rutonde rw’ishyaka riharanira ukwishyira ukizana kwa buri muntu kandi atorerwa kuba umuyobozi wungirije wa komisiyo ihoraho ishinzwe ibibazo bya politiki n’uburinganire.<ref>https://www.bbc.com/gahuza/amakuru/2015/12/151218_rwanda_referendum_dec2015</ref>

Kuva mu Kwakira 2011, yari Umusenateri (Urugereko rwo hejuru) kandi yatowe n'abasenateri kuba Umuyobozi wungirije wa Komisiyo ihoraho ishinzwe ibibazo bya politiki n'imiyoborere myiza.<ref>https://www.womenpoliticalleaders.org/speaker-2021/donatille-mukabalisa/</ref>

